Html: Is there any plans to revisit and update the holy priest module? Currently the only thing that loads up is the disc priest role, and it's got all kinds of issues it seems. Is priest development currently dead then? Or is it just not going to be tackled till MoP?

Yea currently the Healing priest module is dead. TNSe no longer is around so we currently don't have an active dev to work on it. If you know anyone who is a C# programmer (or at least rudimentary knowledge of it) and wants to work, just let us know.

I seriously wish I did, have you guys tried advertising to try and fill the spot? I could post some stuff on MMO champion or something along those lines. I Haven't used Rawr since wrath, but I recall the fine tweaking tools being unmatched in finding a good upgrade and testing different builds.
